=========================================================================
  claude-cli-cloud-run — pre-built Claude Code dev environment
=========================================================================
  Tools:     claude, uv, cargo, rustc, git, gh, vim, tmux, ripgrep, jq
  Workdir:   ~/workspaces  (bind-mounted; clone repos here)

  Start claude:
      claude --dangerously-skip-permissions

  GitHub auth (one of):
      gh auth login                  # interactive
      export GH_TOKEN=ghp_...        # or set GH_TOKEN in .env

  Persisted via mounts: ~/.claude{,.json}, ~/.ssh, ~/.config/gh, ~/workspaces.
=========================================================================
